      "body" : "Thanks for the binaries.\r\n\r\n![win](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/6399679/10641231/9e4b3ed8-7818-11e5-9cef-6b27315039df.png)\r\n\r\n\r\nSadly 98c66cd does not work on windows as mentioned by @dexX7 and here: https://stackoverflow.com/questions/1468022/how-to-specify-monospace-fonts-for-cross-platform-qt-applications\r\n\r\nAlso I can't test HiDPI.\r\n\r\nI will have a look how to fix this...\r\n\r\n\r\n",
